value: Locally in wet grasslands of central Africa
Resident and intra-African migrant, short grass inundated by rains: S Cameroon, Nigeria; SE DRC, E Angola, Zambia, E Zimbabwe; SC Kenya.

breeding habitat short grass, temporarily inundated during rains, eg at edges of rivers, drainage lines & marshes;also grass flats & plains;in W Africa dry grassland;in NE Gabon areas w.largue tussocks in shorter grass.

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip
